```kotlin
application {
    mainClass.set("io.ktor.server.netty.EngineMain")
}
```

</tab>
<tab title="Gradle (Groovy)" group-key="groovy">

```groovy
mainClassName = "io.ktor.server.netty.EngineMain"
```

